---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="clinconvert — XLS / CSV / JSON → FHIR R4">
  <section class="hero container">
    <h1>把病歷資料轉成 <span class="hl">FHIR R4</span> 標準</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      支援 XLS / XLSX / CSV / JSON 輸入。批次上傳幾百個檔，瀏覽器內 Web Worker 並行處理，
      輸出符合 HL7 FHIR R4 規範的 Bundle JSON、NDJSON、Transaction Bundle。
    </p>
    <p class="privacy">
      🔒 <strong>檔案 100% 在你的瀏覽器處理</strong> · 不上傳、不留紀錄 · 並行 Worker Pool
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="container converter-section">
    <div class="converter">

      <!-- Step 1: Upload -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="step-label">Step 1 · 上傳檔案</div>
        <label for="file-input" class="dropzone" id="dropzone">
          <input type="file" id="file-input" accept=".xlsx,.xls,.csv,.json" multiple hidden />
          <div class="dropzone-content">
            <strong>選擇檔案</strong>，或拖拉檔案 / 資料夾到這裡
            <p class="muted">支援 .xlsx · .xls · .csv · .json · 一次幾百個檔沒問題</p>
          </div>
        </label>
        <div class="upload-options">
          <button type="button" class="link-btn" id="pick-folder">📁 改選資料夾</button>
          <input type="file" id="folder-input" webkitdirectory directory multiple hidden />
          <span class="muted samples">
            ｜範例：
            <a href="/sample-data/sample-patients.csv" download>patients.csv</a> ·
            <a href="/sample-data/sample-kdigo-observations.csv" download>observations.csv</a> ·
            <a href="/sample-data/sample-exclincalc.json" download>exclincalc.json</a>
          </span>
        </div>
        <div id="file-info" class="file-info" hidden></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: Processing / Progress -->
      <div class="card" id="step-progress" hidden>
        <div class="step-label">Step 2 · 處理進度</div>
        <div class="progress-row">
          <div class="progress-bar"><div id="progress-fill" class="progress-fill"></div></div>
          <span id="progress-text" class="progress-text">準備中...</span>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-stats" id="progress-stats"></div>
        <button type="button" class="cancel-btn" id="cancel-btn" hidden>取消所有處理</button>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3: Per-file results / mapping preview -->
      <div class="card" id="step-results" hidden>
        <div class="step-label">Step 3 · 各檔結果 + 預覽</div>
        <div id="results-list"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4: Output -->
      <div class="card" id="step-output" hidden>
        <div class="step-label">Step 4 · 下載 FHIR Bundle</div>
        <div class="output-summary" id="output-summary"></div>
        <div class="output-actions">
          <button type="button" data-format="organized" class="primary-cta">📦 完整整理包（zip）</button>
          <button type="button" data-format="collection">⬇ Bundle (collection)</button>
          <button type="button" data-format="transaction">⬇ Transaction Bundle</button>
          <button type="button" data-format="ndjson">⬇ NDJSON</button>
          <button type="button" data-format="zip-per-file" class="secondary">⬇ 每檔分開（zip）</button>
        </div>
        <p class="muted output-hint">
          💡 <strong>完整整理包</strong>內含：依 resource type 分組、依病人分組、統計報告 (README)、錯誤列表 (errors.csv)、未匹配範本 (unmatched.csv) ── <strong>診所直接用這個</strong>。
        </p>
        <details class="preview">
          <summary>預覽 JSON（前 5000 字）</summary>
          <pre id="output-preview"></pre>
        </details>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="how" class="container">
    <h2>使用方式</h2>
    <ol class="steps">
      <li>
        <strong>上傳檔案 / 資料夾</strong>
        <p>XLS / XLSX / CSV / JSON。可一次拖拉幾百個檔，或直接拖整個資料夾。每個 sheet / array 視為一個 dataset。</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>自動套用範本</strong>
        <p>依檔名與 sheet 名稱自動推薦對應 FHIR resource 範本（ExClinCalc / 健保處方箋 / KDIGO 體檢 四種）。Web Worker Pool 並行處理。</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>下載 FHIR Bundle</strong>
        <p>所有 resource 合併成單一 Bundle；或每檔分開、各自獨立的 Bundle 打包成 zip。</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section id="templates" class="container">
    <h2>支援的 FHIR Resource（v1）</h2>
    <ul class="resources">
      <li><code>Patient</code> · 身分、姓名、性別、生日、聯絡方式 <span class="muted">· <a href="https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/patient.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HL7 spec</a></span></li>
      <li><code>Encounter</code> · 就診紀錄、狀態、時間段 <span class="muted">· <a href="https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/encounter.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HL7 spec</a></span></li>
      <li><code>Observation</code> · 檢驗值、生命徵象（LOINC 編碼） <span class="muted">· <a href="https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/observation.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HL7 spec</a></span></li>
    </ul>

    <h3>規劃中（v2 / v3）</h3>
    <ul class="resources muted">
      <li><code>Medication</code> / <code>Condition</code> / <code>Procedure</code></li>
      <li>HL7 v2 message → FHIR R4</li>
      <li>反向轉換：FHIR → XLS</li>
      <li>對接 HAPI FHIR public test server 做 round-trip 驗證</li>
      <li>CLI 版本（給診所 IT 跑 batch script）</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="container context-section">
    <div class="context">
      <h2>關於這個工具</h2>
      <p>
        衛福部 2026 年目標完成全台<strong>醫學中心 FHIR 電子病歷互通</strong>（中山、長庚、馬偕已示範完成）。
        到 2028 年將擴及衛生所與診所。
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>clinconvert 是給「中小型診所、護理之家、研究者」過渡到 FHIR 用的轉換工具</strong>。
        大醫院的 HIS DB → FHIR 用 MIRTH Connect 或 HAPI FHIR；本工具補位「資料還在 Excel 階段」的小規模場景，
        但**架構支援批次處理幾百個檔**（Web Worker Pool 並行）。
      </p>
      <p>設計選擇：</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>瀏覽器本地處理</strong> ── 醫療資料不離開使用者裝置</li>
        <li><strong>Web Worker Pool 並行</strong> ── 主執行緒不卡、可處理大批檔案</li>
        <li><strong>Adapter pattern</strong> ── 容易擴充新的輸入 / 輸出格式</li>
        <li><strong>開源</strong> ── 完整程式碼在 GitHub，歡迎 fork 客製</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .hero { padding: 4rem 20px 2rem; max-width: 800px; }
    .hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hl { color: var(--c-primary); }
    .lead { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--c-text); }
    .privacy { font-size: 0.95rem; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; background: var(--c-success-bg); border-left: 3px solid var(--c-success); border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; color: var(--c-success); }
    section { padding: 2rem 20px; }

    .converter-section { padding-top: 1rem; }
    .converter { display: grid; gap: 1.25rem; }
    .card { padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--c-bg-soft); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); }
    .step-label { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--c-primary); letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.85rem; }

    .dropzone { display: block; padding: 2.5rem 1rem; border: 2px dashed var(--c-border); border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; background: var(--c-bg-card); }
    .dropzone:hover, .dropzone.drag-over { border-color: var(--c-primary); background: var(--c-success-bg); }
    .dropzone strong { color: var(--c-primary); }
    .dropzone p { margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; }

    .upload-options { display: flex; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 0.85rem; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .link-btn { background: none; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--c-text-muted); cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; }
    .link-btn:hover { color: var(--c-primary); border-color: var(--c-primary); }
    .samples a { color: var(--c-primary); }

    .file-info { margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; background: var(--c-bg-card); border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); font-size: 0.9rem; }

    .progress-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; }
    .progress-bar { flex: 1; height: 12px; background: var(--c-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--c-border); border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; }
    .progress-fill { height: 100%; background: var(--c-primary); width: 0%; transition: width 0.2s ease; }
    .progress-text { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--c-text-muted); min-width: 7em; text-align: right; }
    .progress-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(120px, 1fr)); gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .progress-stat { padding: 0.6rem 0.85rem; background: var(--c-bg-card); border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); }
    .progress-stat strong { color: var(--c-text); display: block; font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .progress-stat .label { color: var(--c-text-soft); font-size: 0.78rem; }
    .cancel-btn { margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; background: var(--c-error-bg); color: var(--c-error); border: 1px solid var(--c-error); border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .cancel-btn:hover { background: var(--c-error); color: white; }

    .result-row { padding: 0.85rem 1rem; background: var(--c-bg-card); border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
    .result-row.ok { border-left: 3px solid var(--c-success); }
    .result-row.warn { border-left: 3px solid var(--c-warn); }
    .result-row.err { border-left: 3px solid var(--c-error); }
    .result-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .result-name { font-weight: 600; color: var(--c-text); }
    .result-stats { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--c-text-soft); }
    .result-detail { margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--c-text-muted); }
    .result-detail details { margin-top: 0.5rem; }
    .result-detail summary { cursor: pointer; color: var(--c-primary); font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .errors-list { margin-top: 0.5rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; max-height: 200px; overflow: auto; padding: 0.5rem; background: var(--c-error-bg); border-radius: 4px; }
    .errors-list li { list-style: none; padding: 0.15rem 0; color: var(--c-error); }
    .mapping-preview { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.75rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    .mapping-preview > div { padding: 0.5rem; background: var(--c-bg-soft); border-radius: 4px; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; max-height: 200px; overflow: auto; }
    .mapping-preview .src-label, .mapping-preview .fhir-label { font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--c-text-soft); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .mapping-preview { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .output-summary { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; background: var(--c-bg-card); border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .output-actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .output-actions button { padding: 0.65rem 1rem; background: var(--c-primary); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 6px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s; }
    .output-actions button:hover { background: var(--c-primary-light); }
    .output-actions button.secondary { background: var(--c-bg-card); color: var(--c-text); border: 1px solid var(--c-border); }
    .output-actions button.secondary:hover { border-color: var(--c-primary); color: var(--c-primary); }
    .output-actions button.primary-cta { background: var(--c-accent); font-weight: 700; padding-left: 1.25rem; padding-right: 1.25rem; }
    .output-actions button.primary-cta:hover { background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c-accent) 80%, white); }
    .output-hint { font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .preview { margin-top: 1rem; }
    .preview summary { cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--c-text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .preview pre { max-height: 320px; overflow: auto; font-size: 0.78rem; line-height: 1.5; }

    .steps { list-style: none; counter-reset: step; display: grid; gap: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .steps li { padding-left: 3rem; position: relative; }
    .steps li::before { counter-increment: step; content: counter(step); position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; width: 2rem; height: 2rem; background: var(--c-primary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: grid; place-items: center; font-weight: 700; }
    .resources { list-style: none; display: grid; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .resources li { padding: 0.6rem 0.85rem; background: var(--c-bg-soft); border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); }
    .context { background: var(--c-bg-soft); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; }
    .context ul { padding-left: 1.25em; }
    .context li { color: var(--c-text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.4em; }
  </style>

  <script>
    import { createWorkerPool, recommendedPoolSize } from '../lib/worker-pool';
    import {
      toCollectionBundle,
      toTransactionBundle,
      toNdjson,
      toPrettyJson,
      triggerDownload,
    } from '../lib/output/bundle';
    import { organize, buildOrganizedZip, formatReport, type FileOutcome } from '../lib/output/organizer';
    import type { FhirAnyResource } from '../lib/fhir/types';
    import type { ConvertSuccess, ConvertError, DatasetSummary } from '../workers/converter.worker';

    // === DOM refs ===
    const $file = document.getElementById('file-input') as HTMLInputElement;
    const $folder = document.getElementById('folder-input') as HTMLInputElement;
    const $pickFolder = document.getElementById('pick-folder') as HTMLButtonElement;
    const $dropzone = document.getElementById('dropzone') as HTMLLabelElement;
    const $fileInfo = document.getElementById('file-info') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $stepProgress = document.getElementById('step-progress') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $progressFill = document.getElementById('progress-fill') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $progressText = document.getElementById('progress-text') as HTMLSpanElement;
    const $progressStats = document.getElementById('progress-stats') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $cancelBtn = document.getElementById('cancel-btn') as HTMLButtonElement;
    const $stepResults = document.getElementById('step-results') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $resultsList = document.getElementById('results-list') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $stepOutput = document.getElementById('step-output') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $outputSummary = document.getElementById('output-summary') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $outputPreview = document.getElementById('output-preview') as HTMLPreElement;

    // === State ===
    interface FileResult {
      jobId: string;
      fileName: string;
      status: 'pending' | 'parsing' | 'building' | 'done' | 'error';
      resources: FhirAnyResource[];
      datasets: DatasetSummary[];
      error?: string;
    }
    const results = new Map<string, FileResult>();
    let pool = createWorkerPool(recommendedPoolSize());
    let startTime = 0;

    // Setup pool callbacks
    function setupPool() {
      pool.onProgress((msg) => {
        // Update specific file's status
        const r = results.get(msg.jobId);
        if (r) {
          r.status = msg.phase === 'parse' ? 'parsing' : 'building';
        }
        updateStats();
      });

      pool.onJobComplete((msg) => {
        const r = results.get(msg.jobId);
        if (!r) return;
        if (msg.type === 'success') {
          r.status = 'done';
          r.resources = msg.resources;
          r.datasets = msg.datasets;
        } else {
          r.status = 'error';
          r.error = msg.message;
        }
        renderResults();
        updateOutput();
        updateStats();
      });

      pool.onAllDone(() => {
        $cancelBtn.hidden = true;
        const elapsed = ((performance.now() - startTime) / 1000).toFixed(1);
        $progressText.textContent = `完成 · ${elapsed}s`;
        $progressFill.style.width = '100%';
      });
    }
    setupPool();

    // === Drag & drop（含資料夾遞迴）===
    $dropzone.addEventListener('dragover', (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      $dropzone.classList.add('drag-over');
    });
    $dropzone.addEventListener('dragleave', () => $dropzone.classList.remove('drag-over'));
    $dropzone.addEventListener('drop', async (e: DragEvent) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      $dropzone.classList.remove('drag-over');
      const items = e.dataTransfer?.items;
      if (!items) return;
      const files: File[] = [];
      const promises: Promise<void>[] = [];
      for (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {
        const entry = (items[i] as any).webkitGetAsEntry?.();
        if (entry) {
          promises.push(walkEntry(entry, files));
        } else {
          const f = items[i].getAsFile();
          if (f) files.push(f);
        }
      }
      await Promise.all(promises);
      processFiles(files);
    });

    async function walkEntry(entry: any, out: File[]): Promise<void> {
      if (entry.isFile) {
        return new Promise<void>((resolve) => {
          entry.file((file: File) => {
            out.push(file);
            resolve();
          });
        });
      } else if (entry.isDirectory) {
        const reader = entry.createReader();
        return new Promise<void>((resolve) => {
          reader.readEntries(async (entries: any[]) => {
            await Promise.all(entries.map((e) => walkEntry(e, out)));
            resolve();
          });
        });
      }
    }

    $file.addEventListener('change', () => {
      if ($file.files) processFiles(Array.from($file.files));
    });
    $pickFolder.addEventListener('click', () => $folder.click());
    $folder.addEventListener('change', () => {
      if ($folder.files) processFiles(Array.from($folder.files));
    });

    $cancelBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      pool.cancel();
      // Recreate pool for next batch
      pool = createWorkerPool(recommendedPoolSize());
      setupPool();
      $cancelBtn.hidden = true;
      $progressText.textContent = '已取消';
    });

    async function processFiles(rawFiles: File[]) {
      // 過濾出支援的格式
      const supported = rawFiles.filter((f) =>
        /\.(xlsx?|csv|json)$/i.test(f.name)
      );
      if (supported.length === 0) {
        $fileInfo.hidden = false;
        $fileInfo.innerHTML = '<span style="color:var(--c-error)">沒有支援的檔案（需 .xlsx / .xls / .csv / .json）</span>';
        return;
      }

      $fileInfo.hidden = false;
      $fileInfo.innerHTML = `準備處理 <strong>${supported.length}</strong> 個檔案，使用 ${recommendedPoolSize()} 個 Worker 並行...`;

      // Init UI
      results.clear();
      $resultsList.innerHTML = '';
      $stepProgress.hidden = false;
      $stepResults.hidden = false;
      $stepOutput.hidden = true;
      $cancelBtn.hidden = false;
      startTime = performance.now();

      // 預讀 buffer + 建 jobs
      const jobs = await Promise.all(
        supported.map(async (f, i) => {
          const buf = await f.arrayBuffer();
          const isJson = /\.json$/i.test(f.name);
          const jobId = `job-${Date.now()}-${i}`;
          results.set(jobId, {
            jobId,
            fileName: f.name,
            status: 'pending',
            resources: [],
            datasets: [],
          });
          return { jobId, fileName: f.name, buffer: buf, isJson };
        })
      );
      renderResults();
      pool.submit(jobs);
      updateStats();
    }

    function updateStats() {
      const arr = Array.from(results.values());
      const total = arr.length;
      const done = arr.filter((r) => r.status === 'done').length;
      const err = arr.filter((r) => r.status === 'error').length;
      const active = arr.filter((r) => r.status === 'parsing' || r.status === 'building').length;
      const pending = arr.filter((r) => r.status === 'pending').length;
      const completed = done + err;
      const pct = total > 0 ? Math.round((completed / total) * 100) : 0;
      $progressFill.style.width = pct + '%';
      $progressText.textContent = `${completed} / ${total} · ${pct}%`;

      const totalResources = arr.reduce((s, r) => s + r.resources.length, 0);
      const totalErrors = arr.reduce((s, r) => s + r.datasets.reduce((s2, d) => s2 + d.errorRows.length, 0), 0);

      $progressStats.innerHTML = `
        <div class="progress-stat"><strong>${active}</strong><span class="label">處理中</span></div>
        <div class="progress-stat"><strong>${pending}</strong><span class="label">排隊中</span></div>
        <div class="progress-stat"><strong>${done}</strong><span class="label">完成</span></div>
        <div class="progress-stat"><strong>${err}</strong><span class="label">失敗</span></div>
        <div class="progress-stat"><strong>${totalResources}</strong><span class="label">FHIR resource</span></div>
        <div class="progress-stat"><strong>${totalErrors}</strong><span class="label">轉換錯誤列</span></div>
      `;
    }

    function renderResults() {
      const arr = Array.from(results.values());
      $resultsList.innerHTML = arr.map(renderRow).join('');
    }

    function renderRow(r: FileResult): string {
      const klass = r.status === 'error' ? 'err' : r.status === 'done' ? 'ok' : 'warn';
      let detail = '';
      if (r.status === 'error') {
        detail = `<div class="result-detail" style="color:var(--c-error)">${escapeHtml(r.error ?? 'unknown error')}</div>`;
      } else if (r.status === 'done') {
        const totalBuilt = r.datasets.reduce((s, d) => s + d.builtCount, 0);
        const totalErr = r.datasets.reduce((s, d) => s + d.errorRows.length, 0);
        const unmatched = r.datasets.filter((d) => !d.matchedTemplateId).map((d) => d.sourceDescription);
        const errLists = r.datasets.filter((d) => d.errorRows.length > 0);
        detail = `<div class="result-detail">產出 ${totalBuilt} 個 resource${totalErr > 0 ? '，' + totalErr + ' 列錯誤' : ''}`;
        if (unmatched.length > 0) {
          detail += `<br/><span style="color:var(--c-warn)">⚠ 找不到對應範本：${unmatched.map(escapeHtml).join('、')}</span>`;
        }
        if (errLists.length > 0) {
          const items = errLists.flatMap((d) => d.errorRows.slice(0, 30)).map((e) => `<li>${escapeHtml(e.sourceRef)}：${escapeHtml(e.reason)}</li>`).join('');
          detail += `<details><summary>看錯誤列（最多顯示 30 條）</summary><ul class="errors-list">${items}</ul></details>`;
        }
        // Mapping preview：show first record before/after
        if (r.resources.length > 0) {
          const firstResource = r.resources[0];
          detail += `<details><summary>看第一筆轉換預覽（FHIR resource）</summary><div class="mapping-preview"><div><div class="fhir-label">FHIR ${firstResource.resourceType}</div>${escapeHtml(JSON.stringify(firstResource, null, 2))}</div></div></details>`;
        }
        detail += `</div>`;
      } else {
        detail = `<div class="result-detail">${r.status === 'parsing' ? '解析中…' : r.status === 'building' ? '建構 FHIR…' : '排隊中'}</div>`;
      }
      return `
        <div class="result-row ${klass}">
          <div class="result-head">
            <span class="result-name">${escapeHtml(r.fileName)}</span>
            <span class="result-stats">${r.resources.length} resources</span>
          </div>
          ${detail}
        </div>
      `;
    }

    function escapeHtml(s: string): string {
      return s.replace(/&/g, '&amp;').replace(/</g, '&lt;').replace(/>/g, '&gt;').replace(/"/g, '&quot;');
    }

    function allResources(): FhirAnyResource[] {
      const out: FhirAnyResource[] = [];
      for (const r of results.values()) if (r.status === 'done') out.push(...r.resources);
      return out;
    }

    function updateOutput() {
      const res = allResources();
      if (res.length === 0) {
        $stepOutput.hidden = true;
        return;
      }
      $stepOutput.hidden = false;
      const byType = res.reduce<Record<string, number>>((acc, r) => {
        acc[r.resourceType] = (acc[r.resourceType] ?? 0) + 1;
        return acc;
      }, {});
      $outputSummary.innerHTML = `共 <strong>${res.length}</strong> 個 FHIR resource：${Object.entries(byType).map(([k, v]) => `${k} × ${v}`).join(' · ')}`;
      const bundle = toCollectionBundle(res);
      const json = toPrettyJson(bundle);
      $outputPreview.textContent = json.slice(0, 5000) + (json.length > 5000 ? '\n... (truncated for preview, full output in download)' : '');
    }

    // Download handlers
    document.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>('.output-actions button').forEach((btn) => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', async () => {
        const res = allResources();
        if (res.length === 0) return;
        const fmt = btn.dataset.format ?? 'collection';
        const ts = new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 19).replace(/[T:]/g, '-');
        if (fmt === 'collection') {
          triggerDownload(toPrettyJson(toCollectionBundle(res)), `fhir-bundle-${ts}.json`, 'application/fhir+json');
        } else if (fmt === 'transaction') {
          triggerDownload(toPrettyJson(toTransactionBundle(res)), `fhir-transaction-${ts}.json`, 'application/fhir+json');
        } else if (fmt === 'ndjson') {
          triggerDownload(toNdjson(res), `fhir-${ts}.ndjson`, 'application/x-ndjson');
        } else if (fmt === 'zip-per-file') {
          // Per-file mode：每個 input file 一個 Bundle，打包成 zip
          const JSZip = (await import('jszip')).default;
          const zip = new JSZip();
          for (const r of results.values()) {
            if (r.status === 'done' && r.resources.length > 0) {
              const bundle = toCollectionBundle(r.resources);
              const baseName = r.fileName.replace(/\.[^.]+$/, '') + '.fhir.json';
              zip.file(baseName, toPrettyJson(bundle));
            }
          }
          const blob = await zip.generateAsync({ type: 'blob' });
          downloadBlob(blob, `fhir-bundles-${ts}.zip`);
        } else if (fmt === 'organized') {
          // 完整整理包：分類、分病人、統計、錯誤
          const outcomes: FileOutcome[] = Array.from(results.values()).map((r) => ({
            fileName: r.fileName,
            status: r.status === 'done' ? 'done' : 'error',
            resources: r.resources,
            datasets: r.datasets,
            error: r.error,
          }));
          const elapsed = performance.now() - startTime;
          const organized = organize(outcomes, elapsed);
          const blob = await buildOrganizedZip(organized, 'zh');
          downloadBlob(blob, `clinconvert-organized-${ts}.zip`);
        }
      });
    });

    function downloadBlob(blob: Blob, filename: string) {
      const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
      const a = document.createElement('a');
      a.href = url;
      a.download = filename;
      document.body.appendChild(a);
      a.click();
      document.body.removeChild(a);
      URL.revokeObjectURL(url);
    }
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
